      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;lead text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 !mb-9 text-xl&#34;&gt;&#xA;  A record of the tinkering and trials along the way—the path that made me who I am today.&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Preface&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;preface&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#preface&#34; aria-label=&#34;锚点&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Next semester marks the start of the graduate school nomination season. Looking back at the past three years, I’ve certainly been a &amp;ldquo;tinkerer.&amp;rdquo; Some of these trials and errors are already starting to blur in my memory. I’m using the quiet of this winter break to document these fragments—partly as a keepsake, and partly as raw material for my personal statement.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
